## Startup Sequence

1. Load `NotifierConfig` from environment
2. Setup logging
3. Connect to Redis
4. Create `EventsSubscriber` and connect to NATS
5. Create `ProgramSettingsProvider`
6. Create `SimpleBatchManager` and `ApiConfigProvider`
7. Resolve handlers per program from the API (with Redis cache) when processing events
8. Start batch recovery background task
9. Start main event processing loop

